Package twao.villages

Class Village

  • java.lang.Object
    • twao.villages.Village
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AllyVillage, TargetVillage
    public class Village
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents given Village. It is meant to be used as List<Village> member so it implements 'relativeDistance' methods to cooperate with them.
